  "texts": [
    "In addition, we provide detailed information about the dataset and evaluation criteria.",
    "In contrast to previous studies, we present recent research based on deep learning methods that focus on object detection for different tasks in traffic scenes.",
    "Our review stands out for its comprehensive, in-depth analysis of object detection in traffic scenes.",
    "We also present a comprehensive overview of existing datasets in traffic scenarios and summarise various approaches based on different application scenarios.",
    "ContributionIn this paper, our main contributions can be summarized as follows:1) The general purpose of basic studies is to analyze the progress of arithmetic and to understand the latest information in the area.2) In the context of object detection in traffic scenarios, we comprehensively summarize three primary application scenarios, including traffic sign detection, pedestrian detection, and vehicle detection."
